# Codex Infra Transcript Review

Joel did a large infra pass on 2026-06-17. The daily postboot check should review recent Codex transcripts so completed infra work is not stranded in chat.

## Method

First attempt:

```sh
joelclaw sessions search "NAS three-body Flagg MTU MinIO Convex Postgres postboot" --source typesense --machine all --runtime codex --limit 10 --extract
joelclaw sessions search "infra central migration Flagg Panda NAS MinIO Convex" --source typesense --machine all --runtime codex --limit 10 --extract
```

Result: Typesense Codex search returned stale or irrelevant hits for today's infra work. The useful review came from bounded local raw Codex metadata and recent `rollout-*.jsonl` files under `~/.codex`.

Do not dump raw transcripts. Use session ids, filenames, final answers, commands, receipts, and bounded snippets.

